00130 DdNode *
00131 Cudd_PrioritySelect(
00132   DdManager * dd /* manager */,
00133   DdNode * R /* BDD of the relation */,
00134   DdNode ** x /* array of x variables */,
00135   DdNode ** y /* array of y variables */,
00136   DdNode ** z /* array of z variables (optional: may be NULL) */,
00137   DdNode * Pi /* BDD of the priority function (optional: may be NULL) */,
00138   int  n /* size of x, y, and z */,
00139   DdNode * (*Pifunc)(DdManager *, int, DdNode **, DdNode **, DdNode **) /* function used to build Pi if it is NULL */)
00140 {
00141     DdNode *res = NULL;
00142     DdNode *zcube = NULL;
00143     DdNode *Rxz, *Q;
00144     int createdZ = 0;
00145     int createdPi = 0;
00146     int i;
00147 
00148     /* Create z variables if needed. */
00149     if (z == NULL) {
00150         if (Pi != NULL) return(NULL);
00151         z = ALLOC(DdNode *,n);
00152         if (z == NULL) {
00153             dd->errorCode = CUDD_MEMORY_OUT;
00154             return(NULL);
00155         }
00156         createdZ = 1;
00157         for (i = 0; i < n; i++) {
00158             if (dd->size >= (int) CUDD_MAXINDEX - 1) goto endgame;
00159             z[i] = cuddUniqueInter(dd,dd->size,dd->one,Cudd_Not(dd->one));
00160             if (z[i] == NULL) goto endgame;
00161         }
00162     }
00163 
00164     /* Create priority function BDD if needed. */
00165     if (Pi == NULL) {
00166         Pi = Pifunc(dd,n,x,y,z);
00167         if (Pi == NULL) goto endgame;
00168         createdPi = 1;
00169         cuddRef(Pi);
00170     }
00171 
00172     /* Initialize abstraction cube. */
00173     zcube = DD_ONE(dd);
00174     cuddRef(zcube);
00175     for (i = n - 1; i >= 0; i--) {
00176         DdNode *tmpp;
00177         tmpp = Cudd_bddAnd(dd,z[i],zcube);
00178         if (tmpp == NULL) goto endgame;
00179         cuddRef(tmpp);
00180         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd,zcube);
00181         zcube = tmpp;
00182     }
00183 
00184     /* Compute subset of (x,y) pairs. */
00185     Rxz = Cudd_bddSwapVariables(dd,R,y,z,n);
00186     if (Rxz == NULL) goto endgame;
00187     cuddRef(Rxz);
00188     Q = Cudd_bddAndAbstract(dd,Rxz,Pi,zcube);
00189     if (Q == NULL) {
00190         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd,Rxz);
00191         goto endgame;
00192     }
00193     cuddRef(Q);
00194     Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd,Rxz);
00195     res = Cudd_bddAnd(dd,R,Cudd_Not(Q));
00196     if (res == NULL) {
00197         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd,Q);
00198         goto endgame;
00199     }
00200     cuddRef(res);
00201     Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd,Q);
00202 
00203 endgame:
00204     if (zcube != NULL) Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd,zcube);
00205     if (createdZ) {
00206         FREE(z);
00207     }
00208     if (createdPi) {
00209         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd,Pi);
00210     }
00211     if (res != NULL) cuddDeref(res);
00212     return(res);
00213 
00214 } /* Cudd_PrioritySelect */

00697 DdNode *
00698 Cudd_CProjection(
00699   DdManager * dd,
00700   DdNode * R,
00701   DdNode * Y)
00702 {
00703     DdNode *res;
00704     DdNode *support;
00705 
00706     if (cuddCheckCube(dd,Y) == 0) {
00707         (void) fprintf(stdout,
00708         "Error: The third argument of Cudd_CProjection should be a cube\n");
00709         return(NULL);
00710     }
00711 
00712     /* Compute the support of Y, which is used by the abstraction step
00713     ** in cuddCProjectionRecur.
00714     */
00715     support = Cudd_Support(dd,Y);
00716     if (support == NULL) return(NULL);
00717     cuddRef(support);
00718 
00719     do {
00720         dd->reordered = 0;

00722     } while (dd->reordered == 1);
00723 
00724     if (res == NULL) {
00725         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd,support);
00726         return(NULL);
00727     }
00728     cuddRef(res);
00729     Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd,support);
00730     cuddDeref(res);
00731 
00732     return(res);

00751 DdNode *
00752 Cudd_addHamming(
00753   DdManager * dd,
00754   DdNode ** xVars,
00755   DdNode ** yVars,
00756   int  nVars)

00758     DdNode  *result,*tempBdd;

00762     result = DD_ZERO(dd);

00764 
00765     for (i = 0; i < nVars; i++) {
00766         tempBdd = Cudd_bddIte(dd,xVars[i],Cudd_Not(yVars[i]),yVars[i]);
00767         if (tempBdd == NULL) {
00768             Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd,result);
00769             return(NULL);
00770         }
00771         cuddRef(tempBdd);
00772         tempAdd = Cudd_BddToAdd(dd,tempBdd);
00773         if (tempAdd == NULL) {
00774             Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd,tempBdd);
00775             Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd,result);
00776             return(NULL);

00778         cuddRef(tempAdd);
00779         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd,tempBdd);
00780         temp = Cudd_addApply(dd,Cudd_addPlus,tempAdd,result);
00781         if (temp == NULL) {
00782             Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd,tempAdd);
00783             Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd,result);
00784             return(NULL);
00785         }
00786         cuddRef(temp);
00787         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd,tempAdd);
00788         Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd,result);

00791 
00792     cuddDeref(result);

00822     DdNode *res, *res1, *res2, *resA;
00823     DdNode *r, *y, *RT, *RE, *YT, *YE, *Yrest, *Ra, *Ran, *Gamma, *Alpha;
00824     unsigned int topR, topY, top, index = 0;
00825     DdNode *one = DD_ONE(dd);
00826 
00827     if (Y == one) return(R);
00828 
00829 #ifdef DD_DEBUG
00830     assert(!Cudd_IsConstant(Y));
00831 #endif
00832 
00833     if (R == Cudd_Not(one)) return(R);
00834 
00835     res = cuddCacheLookup2(dd, Cudd_CProjection, R, Y);
00836     if (res != NULL) return(res);
00837 
00838     r = Cudd_Regular(R);
00839     topR = cuddI(dd,r->index);
00840     y = Cudd_Regular(Y);
00841     topY = cuddI(dd,y->index);
00842 
00843     top = ddMin(topR, topY);
00844 
00845     /* Compute the cofactors of R */
00846     if (topR == top) {
00847         index = r->index;
00848         RT = cuddT(r);
00849         RE = cuddE(r);
00850         if (r != R) {
00851             RT = Cudd_Not(RT); RE = Cudd_Not(RE);
00852         }
00853     } else {
00854         RT = RE = R;
00855     }
00856 
00857     if (topY > top) {
00858         /* Y does not depend on the current top variable.
00859         ** We just need to compute the results on the two cofactors of R
00860         ** and make them the children of a node labeled r->index.
00861         */
00862         res1 = cuddCProjectionRecur(dd,RT,Y,Ysupp);
00863         if (res1 == NULL) return(NULL);
00864         cuddRef(res1);
00865         res2 = cuddCProjectionRecur(dd,RE,Y,Ysupp);
00866         if (res2 == NULL) {
00867             Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd,res1);
00868             return(NULL);
00869         }
00870         cuddRef(res2);
00871         res = cuddBddIteRecur(dd, dd->vars[index], res1, res2);
00872         if (res == NULL) {
00873             Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd,res1);
00874             Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd,res2);
00875             return(NULL);
00876         }
00877         /* If we have reached this point, res1 and res2 are now
00878         ** incorporated in res. cuddDeref is therefore sufficient.
00879         */
00880         cuddDeref(res1);
00881         cuddDeref(res2);
00882     } else {
00883         /* Compute the cofactors of Y */
00884         index = y->index;
00885         YT = cuddT(y);
00886         YE = cuddE(y);
00887         if (y != Y) {
00888             YT = Cudd_Not(YT); YE = Cudd_Not(YE);
00889         }
00890         if (YT == Cudd_Not(one)) {
00891             Alpha  = Cudd_Not(dd->vars[index]);
00892             Yrest = YE;
00893             Ra = RE;
00894             Ran = RT;
00895         } else {
00896             Alpha = dd->vars[index];
00897             Yrest = YT;
00898             Ra = RT;
00899             Ran = RE;
00900         }
00901         Gamma = cuddBddExistAbstractRecur(dd,Ra,cuddT(Ysupp));
00902         if (Gamma == NULL) return(NULL);
00903         if (Gamma == one) {
00904             res1 = cuddCProjectionRecur(dd,Ra,Yrest,cuddT(Ysupp));
00905             if (res1 == NULL) return(NULL);
00906             cuddRef(res1);
00907             res = cuddBddAndRecur(dd, Alpha, res1);
00908             if (res == NULL) {
00909                 Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd,res1);
00910                 return(NULL);
00911             }
00912             cuddDeref(res1);
00913         } else if (Gamma == Cudd_Not(one)) {
00914             res1 = cuddCProjectionRecur(dd,Ran,Yrest,cuddT(Ysupp));
00915             if (res1 == NULL) return(NULL);
00916             cuddRef(res1);
00917             res = cuddBddAndRecur(dd, Cudd_Not(Alpha), res1);
00918             if (res == NULL) {
00919                 Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd,res1);
00920                 return(NULL);
00921             }
00922             cuddDeref(res1);
00923         } else {
00924             cuddRef(Gamma);
00925             resA = cuddCProjectionRecur(dd,Ran,Yrest,cuddT(Ysupp));
00926             if (resA == NULL) {
00927                 Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd,Gamma);
00928                 return(NULL);
00929             }
00930             cuddRef(resA);
00931             res2 = cuddBddAndRecur(dd, Cudd_Not(Gamma), resA);
00932             if (res2 == NULL) {
00933                 Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd,Gamma);
00934                 Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd,resA);
00935                 return(NULL);
00936             }
00937             cuddRef(res2);
00938             Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd,Gamma);
00939             Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd,resA);
00940             res1 = cuddCProjectionRecur(dd,Ra,Yrest,cuddT(Ysupp));
00941             if (res1 == NULL) {
00942                 Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd,res2);
00943                 return(NULL);
00944             }
00945             cuddRef(res1);
00946             res = cuddBddIteRecur(dd, Alpha, res1, res2);
00947             if (res == NULL) {
00948                 Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd,res1);
00949                 Cudd_RecursiveDeref(dd,res2);
00950                 return(NULL);
00951             }
00952             cuddDeref(res1);
00953             cuddDeref(res2);
00954         }
00955     }
00956 
00957     cuddCacheInsert2(dd,Cudd_CProjection,R,Y,res);
00958 
00959     return(res);
00960
